text: Today we lost a true man of God who inspired millions with his words of faith and wisdom. #BillyGraham was an extraordinary faith leader who made an indelible mark on our great nation. Karen and I offer our deepest sympathies to his family during this difficult time.
As we continue to learn more about the horrific situation at the high school in Parkland, FL, my prayers are with the students, teachers, their families, and our first responders.

The House will once again vote to responsibly fund our nation's military for the full year. It's time for Senate Democrats to stop holding this critical funding for our nation's men and women in uniform hostage.

It appears that the train hit a garbage truck. Praying for the individuals in the truck.
Karen, my staff members, and I are all on the train to the GOP conference and we are all safe.
